1
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,600
Sister!

2
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:17,880
Sister!

3
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,280
Sister Gesang!

4
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:22,740
Sister!

5
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,490
How dare you!

6
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:31,050
Swallowed by the Chilam Spider Lily of greatest desire.

7
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,780
I want to see how you

8
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:35,040
can save her.

9
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,640
No future tribulations.

10
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,720
No past lives.

11
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,320
We won't meet again in this life.

12
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,180
The Spider Lily stays parted.

13
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,600
If there is an afterlife,

14
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,520
I won't be

15
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:04,440
a pawn at the mercy of Heaven.

16
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,280
Sister!

17
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,480
High God,

18
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,120
I have completed my duty to find the sword.

19
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,920
I shall return to report.

20
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:36,800
Immortal,

21
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,400
you have great magical power.

22
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,200
Please save Sister Gesang!

23
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,680
I told you.

24
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,920
I only came down to the mortal realm to find the sword.

25
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:52,180
It is inconvenient for me to interfere with other matters.

26
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:56,329
It is the tribulation that the High God and this lady must overcome.

27
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,840
Saving people from suffering,

28
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,920
isn't that what immortals are supposed to do?

29
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:02,720
How can you divide it into someone's tribulation?

30
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,520
Everything in the world

31
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,800
has its own destiny

32
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,520
and its own tribulation.

33
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,360
If I interfere,

34
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,520
who knows if the future karma

35
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,480
will be even harder to bear?

36
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,200
A disgrace to our kind.

37
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,520
You have no talent.

38
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,400
Trash fallen from the sky.

39
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,720
And you still dare to dream of becoming an immortal.

40
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,400
You should just die.

41
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,400
You want to join us?

42
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,280
What right does a lowly tree demon have?

43
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,280
Get lost.

44
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:48,960
Otherwise, I'll chop off your roots to go with my wine.

45
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,960
She's a demon.

46
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,440
Beat her to death. Beat her to death.

47
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,080
Suppress.

48
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:29,520
Since the evil has taken root, what use are you?

49
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,580
What are you doing?

50
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,530
She has turned into a demon.

51
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,840
Before she fully awakens,

52
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:48,170
we must kill this tree demon to prevent future troubles.

53
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,810
Don't be soft-hearted.

54
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,460
Are you questioning my judgment?

55
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:59,240
I wouldn't dare.

56
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:05,880
Master,

57
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,960
you will save Sister Gesang,

58
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:08,560
right?

59
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,520
Tu Luohua's demonic power is extremely strong.

60
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,640
These demon flowers

61
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,920
have condensed countless resentful energy.

62
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,920
Trying to save her

63
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,120
is practically impossible.

64
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,530
With ordinary methods,

65
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,080
it's indeed hard to save her.

66
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:25,620
Master,

67
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,240
do you mean there is another way?

68
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,760
Master.

69
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,440
Sister Gesang is a good person.

70
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,000
Oh no,

71
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,159
a good demon.

72
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,120
She was just trying to save us

73
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,380
and got badly injured.

74
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,320
I beg you.

75
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,960
Please save my sister.

76
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,800
Sister!

77
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,600
This demonic aura

78
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,720
cannot be eliminated without Heavenly Thunder.

79
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,780
Heavenly Thunder?

80
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,920
If it strikes now,

81
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,840
wouldn't her soul be destroyed?

82
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,240
Take them to a safe place.

83
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,760
Bai Jingqing,

84
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,120
when hanging the bell on the plum tree,

85
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,000
once said,

86
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:56,040
A thought of longing can overcome the cold.

87
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,640
Today, this protective spiritual tree...

88
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,440
Why can't I redeem her?

89
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,220
Thunder spell.

90
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,170
Heavenly tribulation.

91
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,460
Master.

92
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,260
Don't move.

93
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,880
What is Master doing?

94
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,930
He is going to use the thunder spell

95
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:14,120
to redeem Gesang's demonic nature.

96
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:16,760
If Gesang directly receives this thunder spell,

97
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,240
she will surely turn to ashes.

98
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,000
He wants to use himself as a lightning rod

99
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,860
to bear most of the damage for her.

100
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,320
Can we

101
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,600
do anything to help him?

102
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,840
Help him?

103
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,440
Heavenly thunder is meant to punish immortals and demons.

104
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,900
You and I are both mortals.

105
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,360
Touching it means certain death.

106
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,800
Child.

107
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,640
Go check on her.

108
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,290
She's alive.

109
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,060
Sister Gesang is still alive!

110
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,000
Good.

111
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,320
It hurts.

112
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,400
Why does it hurt so much?

113
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,960
What happened to me?

114
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,880
Brother Qingxuan.

115
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,100
Sister Gesang,

116
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:00,560
Master saved you.

117
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,000
You were infected by Tu Luohua's demon flower.

118
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,560
Master drew the heavenly thunder

119
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,120
and used himself as a conductor

120
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:08,320
to eliminate the demonic nature in you.

121
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,640
Why

122
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:29,960
did you pay such a huge price to save me?

123
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:31,680
You said

124
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:33,920
if demons do evil,

125
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,600
you would never tolerate it.

126
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:39,760
You once said

127
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,200
that a tree's seed

128
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,840
wherever it lands,

129
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,720
it will take root and sprout.

130
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,900
I have guarded Sanshanliu

131
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:52,520
for hundreds of thousands of years.

132
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,240
I've seen countless truth-seekers

133
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:57,780
who, in order to become immortal,

134
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,660
are willing to give up all emotions and desires.

135
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,200
Only one person

136
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:06,160
was willing to give up the path to immortality

137
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,760
to keep a thought of longing.

138
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:12,460
The places she passed through

139
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,490
have a bit more vitality

140
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:16,920
than other places.

141
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,000
Just now,

142
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,160
when you saved that child,

143
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:26,050
you had no evil thoughts in your heart.

144
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:30,000
You sacrificed yourself to save all living beings,

145
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,800
and so did I.

146
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:33,640
That's all.

147
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:47,570
Thank you for saving me, High Immortal Qingxuan.

148
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:49,320
I, Gesang,

149
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,720
cannot repay you.

150
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,400
Why does my body

151
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,040
feel a little strange?

152
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,930
You were injured by the heavenly thunder.

153
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:15,960
It is already not easy

154
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:18,080
to keep you alive.

155
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,280
I...

156
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,600
I lost all my magic power.

157
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,760
It is already very hard

158
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,570
to keep your human form.

159
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:54,400
I know a place

160
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:57,010
with a spiritual spring

161
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,450
that can revive dead trees.

162
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:03,440
Whether it can help you regain your demonic power

163
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,700
depends on whether you

164
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:08,180
are willing to take root in this world again.

165
00:15:29,160 --> 00:15:29,960
If you want,

166
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:32,320
follow me.

167
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,720
Although we had your help,

168
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,880
we eliminated the four great demons

169
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,690
and wiped out Tu Luohua's lair.

170
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:16,360
No matter how you look at it,

171
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:18,240
it's quite a heroic feat, right?

172
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,240
Grandmaster,

173
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:23,280
I, Hu San,

174
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,490
shall take my leave now.

175
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:27,360
Mr. Hu,

176
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:29,000
are you sure you won't come with us?

177
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,120
The road ahead is dangerous.

178
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:32,240
It'd be safer if we traveled together.

179
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,200
As you know,

180
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,000
I was sent by His Majesty.

181
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,840
Now that the great demon of Tushan has been eliminated,

182
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:39,000
I must announce it to the world.

183
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:39,890
Besides,

184
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,970
I have to escort Miss Yezi home.

185
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,180
If fate allows,

186
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:45,360
we shall definitely meet again.

187
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:47,360
You care for the common people

188
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,840
and save them from suffering.

189
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,600
I hope you keep this original intention.

190
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,440
Given time,

191
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:54,320
you will surely achieve greatness.

192
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,360
Thank you for your guidance, grandmaster.

193
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:57,920
Feilu.

194
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,640
Learn well from my grandmaster.

195
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,000
Cultivate your mind

196
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:02,860
and your magic.

197
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:06,400
If there's a chance in the future,

198
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,520
you can come work at the Directorate of Astronomy.

199
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,359
I'll pass.

200
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:10,720
I want to follow my master,

201
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,760
roam the world with my sword,

202
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:12,640
and uphold justice.

203
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,160
Okay.

204
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:15,359
Miss Gesang,

205
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:19,200
then I wish you and grandmaster

206
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,200
a speedy

207
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:23,560
recovery.

208
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,400
Recovery.

209
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:28,760
Farewell.

210
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,040
Farewell.

211
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,300
Sister Gesang.

212
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,120
You were injured by heavenly lightning.

213
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:44,640
How did you recover so quickly?

214
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:45,280
Could it be

215
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,640
that you were struck into lightning wood?

216
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,720
You need a beating.

217
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:50,120
Just kidding.

218
00:17:51,800 --> 00:17:52,440
However,

219
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,640
this matter is indeed strange.

220
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,600
You were injured by heavenly lightning

221
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,930
and lost all your magic,

222
00:17:57,960 --> 00:18:00,090
yet your energy recovered so quickly.

223
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:01,320
Indeed.

224
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:05,120
Right.

225
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,080
You mentioned before

226
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:08,980
that you fell from the sky.

227
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,100
That's what my mother told me.

228
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:19,680
Break!

229
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,560
I see.

230
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,580
What about you?

231
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,520
The road ahead is long

232
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:31,980
and extremely dangerous.

233
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:33,280
Are you sure you want to follow me?

234
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:33,740
Master,

235
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,360
don't even think about getting rid of me.

236
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:36,240
By the way, Master,

237
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,300
where are we going?

238
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,040
Qingqiu.

239
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,240
No matter where we go,

240
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:57,160
I will follow brother Qingxuan.

241
00:18:59,160 --> 00:18:59,960
Let's go.

242
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,080
Master.

243
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,240
Who is in Qingqiu?

244
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,600
Is your family there?

245
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,080
None of your business.
